"'''Disapproval'''" is a narrative written by [[August Hahn]] and [[Cynthia Hahn]] as a tie-in to the [[Living Force (roleplaying campaign)|Living Force]] campaign. It was published on the [[Wizards of the Coast]] website on [[December 23]], [[2004]] and described an encounter between [[Darrus Jeht/Legends|Darrus Jeht]] and a drunk [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] at the [[Crosstown Bar|Crosstown]] cantina on [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]]. The encounter was related by a member of the [[Cularin Militia]].

In the context of the Living Force campaign, any Jedi Master player character with five Dark Side points was demoted to Jedi Knight, and any Knight with three Dark Side points was demoted to Padawan.

